title: पुनःपरीक्षण की अधिकतम संख्या
description: विनिर्दिष्ट कतार में अनुसूचित किए गए कार्यों पे पुनःपरीक्षण प्रक्रिया करने की अधिकतम संख्या ।

title: Retry Delay
description: Delay to retry to process tasks scheduled in a specific queue in आई.एस.ओ.-८६०१ कलविधि फॉर्मेट PnDTnHnMn.nS में. ।

title: Maximum Retry Delay
description: Maximal Delay to retry to process tasks scheduled in a specific queue in आई.एस.ओ.-८६०१ कलविधि फॉर्मेट PnDTnHnMn.nS में. Infinite if absent ।

title: Retry Delay Multiplier
description: Multiplier in % that will take effect on top of dcmRetryDelay with dcmMaxRetryDelay to be taken into account ।

title: Retry on Warning
description: Enables retries to process tasks not only on failure but also on a warning outcome status in a specific queue ।

title: Retry IN PROCESS on Startup
description: Indicates to retry tasks left in status IN PROCESS on system start-up ।

title: Delay for purging completed queue messages
description: Delay in आई.एस.ओ.-८६०१ कलविधि फॉर्मेट PnDTnHnMn.nS में after which completed queue messages are purged ।If absent, there is no deletion for that particular queue ।

title: Delay for purging failed queue messages
description: Delay in आई.एस.ओ.-८६०१ कलविधि फॉर्मेट PnDTnHnMn.nS में after which failed queue messages are purged ।If absent, there is no deletion for that particular queue ।

title: Delay for purging warning queue messages
description: Delay in आई.एस.ओ.-८६०१ कलविधि फॉर्मेट PnDTnHnMn.nS में after which warning queue messages are purged ।If absent, there is no deletion for that particular queue ।

title: Delay for purging canceled queue messages
description: Delay in आई.एस.ओ.-८६०१ कलविधि फॉर्मेट PnDTnHnMn.nS में after which canceled queue messages are purged ।If absent, there is no deletion for that particular queue ।

title: Maximum Queue Size
description: Maximal number of scheduled tasks in the queue. If the number of scheduled tasks reaches the limit, an attempt to schedule another tasks will fail ।0 = no limitation ।
